Command Line Todo application
=============================
Command line arguments:
    -la  Lists all the tasks
    -l   List Undone task   
    -a   Adds a new task,for multiple values use ","(-a w , r , q)
    -r   Removes an task (format= -r value)
    -c   Completes an task (format= -c value)
    -u   For undo completes task (format= -u value)
    -cu  change user or create new
    -d   Delete user
    -x   Exit